{{Infobox dungeon |name = Mistralton Cave |image = [[File:Mistralton Cave.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Mistralton Cave. |tokens = 196,500 |location = Unova Route 6 }} '''Mistralton Cave''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
